Regina To is the Head of Operations at test.ai where she oversees daily functions involving people operations, finance, and compliance and ensures that the business runs smoothly.
Software engineering focused on making testing easy for everyone. Experience building automation at Google on the Play Store and Ads teams as well as for the Dropbox and Microsoft.
Improving software quality and user experiences in an ever changing and increasingly fast paced world by creatively melding great people with technology and process efficiency.
Obsessed with software testing at scale.  Tested browsers, operating systems, search engines and apps at Microsoft, Google and uTest. Instilling that passion in AI bots today.
Senior executive with business operations, sales, marketing, product management, professional services and field service responsibilities.  Responsible for high growth cyber security companies.
